description:
Minecraft survival. Planetary Confinement is a Minecraft survival challenge map where you must battle against thirst, hunger, temperature, and of the course the deadly mobs that roam the barren planet.

You must gather and use whatever scraps of resources you can find to survive, thrive, and hopefully one day escape your harsh existence.

Map Download: http://www.minecraftforum.net/forums/mapping-and-modding/maps/2361752-1-8-2-planetary-confinement-the-dunes-a-k-a
